Invocation Name: who parks next
des: Next time you're trying to decide whose turn it is to do just about anything, just ask Alexa for help. For example, if you're trying to decide whose turn it is to park in the assigned space, Alexa can randomly select someone's name from the list.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
